title: Season 3 : Trailer
description:
Up and Vanished returns for Season 3 as host Payne Lindsey heads to North West Montana to search for answers in the 2017 disappearance of Ashley Loring HeavyRunner, a 20-year indigenous woman who vanished from the Blackfeet Nation Indian Reservation.
